column1: Have you ever experienced a terrible occurrence that has impacted you significantly? Examples may include being the victim of armed assault, witnessing a tragedy happen to someone else, surviving a sexual assault, or living through a natural disaster
column2: Do you ever feel that you’ve been affected by feelings of edginess, anxiety, or nerves?
column3: Have you ever experienced an ‘attack’ of fear, anxiety, or panic?
column4: Do feelings of anxiety or discomfort around others bother you?
column5: Have you experienced a week or longer of lower-than-usual interest in activities that you usually enjoy? Examples might include work, exercise, or hobbies.
